---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/globals.css";

const SITE = "https://aquinace.com";
const WA =
	"https://wa.me/51916913623?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20conocer%20el%20token%20de%20aqu%C3%AD%20nace%20%F0%9F%AA%99";

const tokenJsonLd = {
	"@context": "https://schema.org",
	"@type": "WebPage",
	name: "AN Token — El token de aquí nace",
	description:
		"AN es el token de aquí nace, creado para impulsar el proyecto y el ecosistema de aquí nace.",
	url: SITE + "/token",
	inLanguage: "es-PE",
};
---

<Layout
	title="AN Token — El token de aquí nace"
	description="AN es el token de aquí nace, creado para impulsar el proyecto y el ecosistema de aquí nace."
	keywords="token aquí nace, AN token, ecosistema aquí nace, criptomoneda aquí nace, finanzas comunitarias token"
	canonicalPath="/token"
	jsonLd={tokenJsonLd}
>
	<div class="bg-blobs" aria-hidden="true">
		<div class="blob blob-1"></div>
		<div class="blob blob-2"></div>
		<div class="blob blob-3"></div>
	</div>

	<!-- Navigation -->
	<nav class="navbar">
		<div class="navbar-inner">
			<a href="/" class="navbar-brand">
				<span class="wordmark"><span class="wm-a">aquí</span><span class="wm-n">nace</span></span>
			</a>
			<div class="navbar-links">
				<a href="/#inicio" class="navbar-link">Inicio</a>
				<a href="/comunidades-inteligentes" class="navbar-link">Comunidades</a>
				<a href="/#servicios" class="navbar-link">Servicios</a>
				<a href="/blog" class="navbar-link">Blog</a>
				<a href="/token" class="navbar-link">Token</a>
			</div>
			<div class="navbar-actions">
				<a href="/" class="btn-back">← Inicio</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<main class="token-main">
		<!-- Hero -->
		<section class="token-hero">
			<div class="token-logo-wrap">
				<div class="token-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
				<img
					class="token-logo"
					src="/an-token.png"
					alt="AN — token de aquí nace"
					width="1254"
					height="1254"
				/>
			</div>

			<h1>
				<span class="grad-yellow">AN</span>, el token de
				<span class="wordmark"><span class="wm-a">aquí</span><span class="wm-n">nace</span></span>
			</h1>
			<p class="token-lead">
				Aquí nace <strong>AN</strong>: el token creado para
				<strong>impulsar el proyecto</strong> y hacer crecer todo el
				<strong>ecosistema de aquí nace</strong>. Una pieza más de nuestra
				misión: acercar más oportunidades financieras a las comunidades.
			</p>
			<div class="token-cta">
				<a href={WA} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-yellow">
					Quiero enterarme primero
				</a>
				<a href="/#servicios" class="btn-ghost">Conoce la plataforma</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Purpose -->
		<section class="token-section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-head">
					<h2>¿Para qué nace <span class="grad-yellow">AN</span>?</h2>
					<p>Un token pensado para fortalecer a la comunidad y potenciar el crecimiento de todo el ecosistema.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="token-cards">
					<article class="token-card">
						<div class="token-card-ic">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Impulsa el proyecto</h3>
						<p>AN aporta el combustible para acelerar el desarrollo de aquí nace y llegar a más comunidades.</p>
					</article>
					<article class="token-card">
						<div class="token-card-ic">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Fortalece el ecosistema</h3>
						<p>Conecta a personas, asociaciones y aliados dentro de una misma red que crece junta.</p>
					</article>
					<article class="token-card">
						<div class="token-card-ic">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" /></svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Crecimiento compartido</h3>
						<p>El valor que se genera en la plataforma regresa a quienes hacen posible la comunidad.</p>
					</article>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Coming soon band -->
		<section class="token-band">
			<div class="band-orb" aria-hidden="true"></div>
			<div class="container token-band-inner">
				<span class="wordmark on-dark band-mark"><span class="wm-a">aquí</span><span class="wm-n">nace</span></span>
				<h2>El token <span class="grad-yellow">AN</span> llega pronto</h2>
				<p>
					Estamos afinando cada detalle para lanzarlo de forma
					<strong>clara, segura y transparente.</strong> Déjanos tu contacto y
					serás de los primeros en conocerlo.
				</p>
				<a href={WA} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-yellow">Avísame cuando esté listo</a>
				<p class="token-disclaimer">
					AN se encuentra en desarrollo. Esta página es solo informativa y no
					constituye una oferta de inversión.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<!-- Footer -->
	<footer class="site-footer">
		<div class="footer-inner">
			<div class="footer-brand">
				<span class="wordmark"><span class="wm-a">aquí</span><span class="wm-n">nace</span></span>
			</div>
			<p class="footer-copy">© 2026 aquí nace · Tu red financiera para crecer juntos</p>
			<div class="footer-links">
				<a href="/blog" class="footer-link">Blog</a>
				<a href="/privacidad" class="footer-link">Privacidad</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</footer>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* ===== BACKGROUND BLOBS ===== */
	.bg-blobs {
		position: fixed;
		inset: 0;
		pointer-events: none;
		overflow: hidden;
		z-index: -1;
	}
	.blob {
		position: absolute;
		border-radius: 50%;
		filter: blur(140px);
	}
	.blob-1 {
		top: -12%;
		left: 15%;
		width: 620px;
		height: 620px;
		background: rgba(245, 197, 24, 0.12);
	}
	.blob-2 {
		bottom: 10%;
		right: -8%;
		width: 520px;
		height: 520px;
		background: rgba(47, 158, 68, 0.1);
	}
	.blob-3 {
		top: 45%;
		left: -8%;
		width: 420px;
		height: 420px;
		background: rgba(245, 197, 24, 0.08);
	}

	/* ===== NAVBAR ===== */
	.navbar {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		z-index: 50;
		backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(28, 90, 48, 0.08);
	}
	.navbar-inner {
		max-width: 1180px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 14px 24px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 24px;
	}
	.navbar-brand {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 10px;
		text-decoration: none;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	.navbar-brand .wordmark {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}
	.navbar-links {
		display: none;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 30px;
	}
	.navbar-link {
		color: var(--green-forest);
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color 0.25s;
	}
	.navbar-link:hover {
		color: var(--green-bright);
	}
	@media (min-width: 900px) {
		.navbar-links {
			display: flex;
		}
	}
	.btn-back {
		color: var(--green-forest);
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}
	.btn-back:hover {
		color: var(--green-bright);
	}

	/* ===== BUTTONS ===== */
	.btn-yellow {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 10px;
		padding: 14px 28px;
		background: var(--yellow);
		color: #3d2c00;
		font-weight: 700;
		border-radius: 9999px;
		font-size: 1rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		border: none;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(245, 197, 24, 0.35);
	}
	.btn-yellow:hover {
		background: #ffd633;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(245, 197, 24, 0.45);
	}
	.btn-ghost {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 14px 28px;
		background: transparent;
		color: var(--green-forest);
		font-weight: 700;
		border-radius: 9999px;
		font-size: 1rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		border: 2px solid rgba(28, 90, 48, 0.2);
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}
	.btn-ghost:hover {
		border-color: var(--green);
		background: var(--green-soft);
	}

	/* ===== GRADIENT TEXT ===== */
	.grad-yellow {
		background: linear-gradient(110deg, #ffde59, #f5c518);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		color: var(--yellow);
	}

	/* ===== TOKEN HERO ===== */
	.token-main {
		padding-top: 0;
	}
	.token-hero {
		max-width: 820px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 150px 24px 40px;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.token-logo-wrap {
		position: relative;
		width: 180px;
		height: 180px;
		margin: 0 auto 34px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}
	.token-glow {
		position: absolute;
		inset: -18%;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245, 197, 24, 0.4), transparent 65%);
		z-index: -1;
	}
	.token-logo {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: contain;
		border-radius: 50%;
		box-shadow: 0 24px 55px rgba(224, 165, 0, 0.32);
		animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
	}
	.token-hero h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5.5vw, 3.6rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		line-height: 1.1;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		color: var(--ink);
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}
	.token-hero h1 .wordmark {
		font-size: 1em;
	}
	.token-lead {
		font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2.2vw, 1.22rem);
		color: var(--muted);
		max-width: 620px;
		margin: 0 auto 34px;
		line-height: 1.75;
	}
	.token-lead strong {
		color: var(--green-800);
	}
	.token-cta {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 14px;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	/* ===== SECTIONS ===== */
	.token-section {
		padding: 80px 24px;
	}
	.container {
		max-width: 1180px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.section-head {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 48px;
	}
	.section-head h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.7rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		color: var(--ink);
		margin-bottom: 14px;
	}
	.section-head p {
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		max-width: 560px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.token-cards {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		gap: 22px;
	}
	@media (min-width: 800px) {
		.token-cards {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		}
	}
	.token-card {
		padding: 30px;
		border-radius: 20px;
		background: var(--cream-2);
		border: 1px solid var(--line);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(28, 90, 48, 0.05);
		transition: all 0.4s;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.token-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		border-color: rgba(245, 197, 24, 0.45);
		box-shadow: 0 24px 44px rgba(224, 165, 0, 0.12);
	}
	.token-card-ic {
		width: 56px;
		height: 56px;
		border-radius: 16px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		margin: 0 auto 18px;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffde59, #f5c518);
		color: #7a4a00;
	}
	.token-card-ic svg {
		width: 26px;
		height: 26px;
	}
	.token-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--ink);
		margin-bottom: 10px;
	}
	.token-card p {
		color: var(--muted);
		line-height: 1.65;
	}

	/* ===== BAND ===== */
	.token-band {
		position: relative;
		padding: 84px 24px;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f3d21 0%, #1c5a30 55%, #226a38 100%);
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.band-orb {
		position: absolute;
		right: -12%;
		top: -20%;
		width: 560px;
		height: 560px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245, 197, 24, 0.28), transparent 62%);
		pointer-events: none;
	}
	.token-band-inner {
		position: relative;
		max-width: 680px;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.band-mark {
		font-size: 1.9rem;
		display: inline-block;
		margin-bottom: 18px;
	}
	.token-band-inner h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		color: #fff;
		line-height: 1.12;
		margin-bottom: 18px;
	}
	.token-band-inner > p {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
		font-size: 1.12rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		max-width: 540px;
		margin: 0 auto 30px;
	}
	.token-band-inner > p strong {
		color: var(--yellow);
	}
	.token-disclaimer {
		margin-top: 26px;
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
		max-width: 520px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	/* ===== FOOTER ===== */
	.site-footer {
		padding: 44px 24px;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
		background: var(--cream);
	}
	.footer-inner {
		max-width: 1180px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 16px;
		text-align: center;
	}
	@media (min-width: 760px) {
		.footer-inner {
			flex-direction: row;
			justify-content: space-between;
			text-align: left;
		}
	}
	.footer-brand .wordmark {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
	}
	.footer-copy {
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}
	.footer-links {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 22px;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		justify-content: center;
	}
	.footer-link {
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color 0.3s;
	}
	.footer-link:hover {
		color: var(--green);
	}

	/* ===== ANIMATIONS ===== */
	@keyframes float {
		0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
		50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
	}
	@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
		.token-logo {
			animation: none !important;
		}
	}
</style>
